asset.hookText:
DKNY Spring/Summer 2014 ft Rita Ora, Karlie Kloss | New York Fashion Week NYFW 

http://www.FashionTV.com/videos NEW YORK - FashionTV grabs a seat in the front row at DKNY Spring/Summer 2014 Collection at Mercedes-Benz Fashion Week New York. Celebrating its 25th anniversary, DKNY showed no signs of its age this season. Models hit the catwalk sporting the DKNY signature urban style wearing baseball caps, overalls, and anoraks down the runway. And while regular model faces such as Karlie Kloss, Joan Smalls, and Chanel Iman starred in Donna Karan's diffusion line show, Rita Ora set the twittersphere alight when she took to the stage and closed the Spring 2014 show.


Appearances: Karlie Kloss, Joan Smalls, Chanel Iman, Rita Ora, Grace Mahary, Kel Markey, Donna Karen
